          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total correction factor of the activity is given",
                "by F = fs*fc*fg. fs, fc, and fg are the correction",
                "factors for the selfabsorption of the sample for a",
                "given gamma energy, the coincident sum-effect of",
                "cascade gamma-rays in the investigated nuclide and in",
                "the counting geometry. Correction factors for the",
                "self-absorption of the sample at 253.7 and 361.2 keV",
                "gamma-rays are 1.083, 1.069 for sample 1 (0.3492 cm),",
                "1.062, 1.051 for sample 2 (0.2621 cm), and 1.083,",
                "1.069 for sample 3 (0.3492 cm)."
              ]
            }
          ],
